sequenceDiagram
    participant O as Orchestrator
    participant P as Policy Engine
    participant H as HITL
    participant T as Tool Runtime
    participant A as Audit Store
    O->>P: subject, action, resource, context, policy_version
    P-->>O: require_approval + obligations + decision_id
    O->>H: immutable action_digest + reason + expiry
    H-->>O: approval_id + approver + scope
    O->>P: resume with approval evidence
    P-->>O: allow / deny after revalidation
    O->>T: authorized invocation + obligations
    T-->>O: typed observation
    P->>A: append policy decision
    H->>A: append approval event
    T->>A: append execution outcome
